       </div><!--kg-card-end: html--><p>We have a problem: the word embeddings we use are a bit too noisy. The word embeddings are usually trained on large text corpora crawled from the internet, such as Wikipedia, the Common Crawl project or from CoNLL 2017 dataset (this is the one used above). The problem with these large corpuses is that they are not perfectly cleaned. For example "-pound" is considered a word. Let's try the CC embeddings:</p><!--kg-card-begin: html--> <div>
